snippet.title: Amber Marshall announces Heartland Season 15!  It's happening!
snippet.description:
Heartland will return with Season 15 to CBC and CBC gem on Sunday, October 17! 

Stream Heartland on CBC Gem: https://gem.cbc.ca/season/heartland/season-14/59d37811-35a3-4a2a-bb63-57fd5b0f2a5d?cmp=scripted_gem

Connect With Heartland on CBC:
Facebook: http://bit.ly/HeartlandOnFacebook
Twitter: http://bit.ly/HeartlandOnTwitter
Official Instagram: http://bit.ly/HeartlandOnInstagram
Georgie's Instagram: http://bit.ly/GeorgieOnInstagram
YouTube: http://bit.ly/HeartlandOnYoutube
#heartlandseason15 #iloveheartland #ambermarshall
